    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "usp_GetBillingPeriodsOfAllPublishedReportsOfSelectedAgency",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve billing periods associated with published reports for a specified agency. It primarily fetches the most recent billing period from a specific table and combines it with distinct billing periods from another table, filtered by agency and time constraints. The results are ordered in descending order of billing periods."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "2. Complexity Level: Medium"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure involves multiple SQL operations, including a "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "UNION",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "JOIN",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", and conditional logic within the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "WHERE",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " clause. It also uses a transaction isolation level setting and handles potential null values with "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "ISNULL",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ". These elements contribute to a medium complexity level."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "3. Input Parameters"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "@AgencyAccessFolder AS VARCHAR(13)",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": This parameter specifies the agency's access folder. It is used to filter the results based on the agency's identifier. If the parameter is set to '*', it acts as a wildcard, effectively removing the filter for agency-specific data."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "4. Business Logic and Workflow"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "orderedList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Transaction Isolation Level",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The procedure sets the transaction isolation level to "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "READ UNCOMMITTED",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", allowing it to read uncommitted changes from other transactions. This can help improve performance by reducing locking overhead but at the risk of reading dirty data."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Retrieve Latest Billing Period",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": It declares a variable "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "@BillingPeriod",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " and assigns it the maximum billing period from the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Published.AccountMeterLevelRawDataForCurrentPeriod",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " table. This represents the most recent billing period available."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Union of Billing Periods",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The procedure constructs a result set that includes:"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "bulletList",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "listItem",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "The latest billing period from the "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "Published.AccountMeterLevelRawDataForCurrentPeriod",
                          "marks": [
                            {
                              "type": "code"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "listItem",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "Distinct billing periods from the "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "ContentManagement.DocumentEndOfMonth",
                          "marks": [
                            {
                              "type": "code"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": " table, joined with "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "Scheduler.DistributionReportArchive",
                          "marks": [
                            {
                              "type": "code"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": " to ensure only relevant records are considered. The "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "ISNULL",
                          "marks": [
                            {
                              "type": "code"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": " function ensures that if a billing period is null, it defaults to the latest billing period."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Filtering and Ordering",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The results are filtered to include only those billing periods within the last 35 months and matching the specified agency access folder. The final result set is ordered by billing period in descending order."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
